	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The glacier bear can be found in the everfrost caverins. If you go down on the ice near megans tower you will see a hole in the ice. Cast enduring breath and swim due north. You will arrive on the undergroud caverin. You will need to take out the goblin diver, and then proceed through the caverns to find the glacier bear.<BR>
<BR>
He is huge, about 3 times the size of Icebear. Conned blue to me at 31. Resists all cold spells.<BR>
Hint: He is an animal (the only animal in the cavern), shaman have the ability to track this beast.  He swims fast, and will come out of that dinky little hole.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
