	<tr>
		
			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have camped the bear several times and have gotten my totemic helm.  This is my opinion on the glacier ice bear.  The spawn has to be at least every 8 hours with wandering Ice bone skels as placeholders.  Killing the ice bones at the huts doesn't seem to make the spawn go any faster but it does give you something to do besides go insane waiting on the bear to spawn.  The bear is the same size as Iceberg.  I think since it's in a cave it just appears to be larger to some people.  Sense animal is a good shaman spell to cast to see if the bear is anywhere in the cave.  Like the previous post said that spell can be bought in Oasis.  Also if you get in a bind you can use befriend animal on the glacier bear and make it your pet for a little while you gain some mana back to finish it off.  However befriend animal is a level 29 spell and most level 29's should be able to kill the bear without it.  Good luck!
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
									
